messages.messageBody:
In a message dated 1/19/2004 11:51:44 AM Eastern Standard Time,
UnschoolingDiscussion@yahoogroups.com writes:
I am very ticklish and hate being tickled, I would rather someone hit me than
tickle me, I find it painful even though I may be laughing.
Laura<<<


I had an uncle who wouldn't stop. I MADE myself not ticklish because I hated
him so!

My boys LOVE to be tickled, but one "stop" ends it----until they say "start"
again! <g>

~Kellt, the unticklish
